[3] Australia (Queensland, New South Wales)
Date: Tue 7 Mar 2017 6:03 PM
Source: News, Australian Associated Press [edited]
http://www.news.com.au/national/breaking-news/concern-over-measles-meningococcal-cases/news-story/4d0f839947cedf16a088c5560b2dde81


Concern over measles, meningococcal cases
-----------------------------------------
A confirmed case of measles on Brisbane's southside last month [February 2017] and a meningococcal case at a childcare centre on Bribie Island has prompted warnings from health authorities.

Queensland Health says a large number of people were potentially exposed when a person infected by measles visited Morningside Tennis Centre, Hampton swim school and Morningside Woolworths late last month.

[byline: Stuart Layt]

